<div class="container">
    <h1>About FPT Long Chau Pharmacy</h1>

    <section id="about-us">
        <h2>I. About Us</h2>
        <p>
            A subsidiary of FPT Digital Retail Joint Stock Company, a member of FPT Corporation, FPT Long Chau Pharmacy is one of the leading and prestigious pharmaceutical retail chains in Vietnam. With over 1,000 pharmacies in more than 63 provinces and cities (as of the end of 2022), FPT Long Chau specializes in providing a diverse range of prescription and over-the-counter drugs, functional foods, medical equipment, cosmetics, and various healthcare and daily consumer products.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="mission">
        <h2>II. Mission</h2>
        <p>
            FPT Long Chau Pharmacy system always aspires to care for and serve the community's health with the best quality and reasonable prices.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section id="core-values">
        <h2>III. Core Values</h2>
        <ol>
            <li>
                <h3>Quality - Leading Prestige</h3>
                <p>
                    All pharmacies within the system meet Good Pharmacy Practice (GPP) standards, with a team of highly qualified and experienced pharmacists. We are committed to advising customers based on the "4 Rights" criteria:
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Right drug</li>
                    <li>Right dose</li>
                    <li>Right way</li>
                    <li>Right price</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    All drugs and products at FPT Long Chau Pharmacy are sourced directly from manufacturers, undergo rigorous quality control processes, and are sold at the listed price.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>Customer-Centric</h3>
                <p>
                    FPT Long Chau Pharmacy continuously improves service quality from the smallest details, aiming to enhance customer experience and bring the highest satisfaction to our valued customers.
                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Fast drug consultation</li>
                    <li>Support for returns and exchanges within 30 days</li>
                    <li>Home delivery</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </section>

    <section id="milestones">
        <h2>IV. Milestones</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>2022: Surpassed 1,000 pharmacies in 63 provinces and cities nationwide</li>
            <li>2021: Surpassed 400 pharmacies in 53 provinces and cities nationwide</li>
            <li>2020: Surpassed 200 pharmacies in 50 provinces and cities nationwide</li>
            <li>2019: Expanded with 32 pharmacies in 5 provinces and cities</li>
            <li>2017: Officially became a subsidiary of FPT Corporation with 8 pharmacies in Ho Chi Minh City</li>
            <li>2007: Established with nearly 20 years of experience in the pharmaceutical retail industry</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
</div>
